lyrics:
[Verse]
There's a sneer in your smile, so cold and sly
Mockery veiled, behind those cunning eyes
Taunts that cut deep, try as I might
Laughter fills my soul, I won't go down without a fight

[Chorus]
Oh, the sneer may sting, but I won't back down
Mock me all you want, but I'll wear my crown
I'll rise above the hate, standing tall and proud
With laughter in my soul, I'll silence every doubt
style: a "Turkish Rap" in the "Gucci Gang" style
